        "derivation": "Midpoint of $AC = (\\frac{1+6}{2}, \\frac{2+6}{2}) = (3.5, 4) \\\\ \\frac{4+x}{2} = 3.5 \\Rightarrow x = 3 \\\\ \\frac{3+y}{2} = 4 \\Rightarrow y = 5"
